data.title: Action Type Code
data.data_values: A: Artillery; B: Base Defense; G: Infantry; R: Reconnaissance Bn
data.definition: Specifies the type of military operation of the action being reported.

data.title: Tactical Area
data.definition: Identifies a specific tactical area of operation in which the action took place.

data.title: Julian Date - Year
data.definition: Identifies the year in which the reported action occurred. The '6', first digit value is generated by the preprocessor and prefixed to form part of the record id.

data.title: Julian Date - Days
data.definition: Identifies the day, in Julian date notation, in which the reported action occurred.

data.title: Julian Date
data.definition: Identifies the Julian notation date of the action. It consists of fields JYEAR and JDAYS.

data.title: Record Sequence
data.definition: Provides a space in the record ID in which to sequence an overflow record.

data.title: Calendar Month
data.definition: Month-of-the-year identification of the action.

data.title: Calendar Day
data.definition: Day-of-the-month identification of the action.

data.title: Calendar Date
data.definition: Calendar date notation of the action. Consists of fields MONTH and DAY.

data.title: Calendar Quarter
data.definition: Year quarter notation of the action

data.title: Unit Size
data.definition: The size of the friendly unit involved in the reported action.

data.title: Observation Post/Listening Post/Sightings/Clear-Day
data.definition: If ACTYPE is 'G' or 'B' and USIZE is 'CO', data represents clearing actions. If ACTYPE is 'G' or 'B' and USIZE is not 'CO', data represents day observation post/listening post action. If ACTYPE is 'R' data represents day sightings.

data.title: Observation Post/Listening Post/Sightings/Clear-Night
data.definition: If ACTYPE is 'G' or 'B' and USIZE is 'CO', data represents night clearing actions. If ACTYPE is 'G' or 'B' and USIZE is not 'CO', data represents night observation post/listening post action. If ACTYPE is 'R' data represents night sightings.

data.title: Observation Post/Listening Post/Sightings/Clear-Both
data.definition: Represents both day (OPLPD) and night (OPLPN) observation post/listening post, sighting, and clearing actions.

data.title: Ambush/Search & Destroy-Day
data.definition: If ACTYPE is 'G' or 'B' and USIZE is 'CO', data represents day search & destroy actions. Otherwise, data represents day ambush actions.

data.title: Ambush/Search & Destroy-Night
data.definition: If ACTYPE is 'G' or 'B' and USIZE is 'CO', data represents night search & destroy actions. Otherwise, data represents night ambush actions.

data.title: Ambush/Search & Destroy-Both
data.definition: Represents both day and night ambush and search & destroy actions.

data.title: Reconnaissance Patrol-Day
data.definition: Represents day reconnaissance patrol actions.

data.title: Reconnaissance Patrol-Night
data.definition: Represents night reconnaissance patrol actions.

data.title: Reconnaissance Patrol-Both
data.definition: Represents both day and night reconnaissance patrol actions.

data.title: Security Patrol/Insertions-Day
data.definition: If ACTYP is 'G' or 'B', data represents day security patrol actions. If ACTYP is 'R' data represents day insertion actions.

data.title: Security Patrol/Insertions-Night
data.definition: If ACTYP is 'G' or 'B', data represents night security patrol actions. If ACTYP is 'R' data represents night insertion actions.

data.title: Security Patrol/Insertions-Both
data.definition: Represents both day and night security patrol and insertion actions.

data.title: Combat Patrol/Retractions-Day
data.definition: If ACTYP is 'G' or 'B', data represents day combat patrol action. If ACTYP is 'R', data represents day retraction actions.

data.title: Combat Patrol/Retractions-Night
data.definition: If ACTYP is 'G' or 'B', data represents night combat patrol action. If ACTYP is 'R', data represents night retraction actions.

data.title: Combat Patrol/Retractions-Both
data.definition: Represents both day and night combat patrol and retraction actions.

data.title: Scout Sniper-Day
data.definition: If ACTYP is 'G' or 'R' and USIZE is 'SS', or ACTYP is 'B', data represents day scout/sniper actions.

data.title: Scout Sniper-Night
data.definition: If ACTYP is 'G' or 'R' and USIZE is 'SS', or ACTYP 'B', data represents night scout/sniper actions.

data.title: Scout Sniper-Both
data.definition: Represents both day and night scout/sniper actions.

data.title: Service
data.definition: Identifies the service of the unit conducting the action being reported.

data.title: Periodic Set 1 Group
data.definition: Represents Periodic Set 1. This group contains all the fields in Periodic Set 1.

data.title: Periodic Set 1 Group with PSSQ1
data.definition: Represents Periodic Set 1, with PSSQ. This group contains all the fields in Periodic Set 1 plus PSSQ1.

data.title: Action Sequence Number
data.definition: An identifying number given to each action by the reporting agency.

data.title: UTM Grid Square Identification
data.definition: Grid square identification portion (xx) of the Universal Transverse Mercator (UTM) coordinate used in locating actions.

data.title: 'East' Coordinates
data.definition: First half of the numeric value (yyy) of the coordinate reading, representing the distance to the east (right) from the origin (lower left-hand corner) of the grid square.

data.title: 'North' Coordinates
data.definition: Second half of the numeric value (zzz) of the coordinate reading, representing the distance to the north (up) from the lower boundary of the grid square.

data.title: UTM Coordinate
data.definition: Full UTM coordinate xx yyy zzz consisting of the UTMSQ (xx), UTMES (yyy), and UTMNO (zzz).

data.title: Date Time Group-Day
data.definition: The day (xx) of the month value (01-31) of the DTG.

data.title: Date Time Group-Hour
data.definition: The hour (yy) of the day value (00-24) of the DTG.

data.title: Date Time Group-Minute
data.definition: The minute (zz) of the hour value (00-59) of the DTG.

data.title: Date Time Group
data.definition: Complete DTG (xxyyzz) consisting of DTGDY (xx), DTGHR (yy), and DTGMN (zz).

data.title: Action Size
data.definition: Identifies the unit size of the action being reported.

data.title: Action Type
data.code: AMB, CDD, CLR, CMB, S/D, SEC, S/S, REC, DEF, L/P, NCD, O/P, PER
data.definition: Identifies the type of action being reported.

data.title: Incident/Contact Group
data.definition: Identifies the size (SIZIC) and type (TYPIC) of action being reported.

data.title: Friendly Losses-Killed in Action
data.definition: Represents the number of friendly personnel killed in the reported action.

data.title: Friendly Losses-Wounded in Action
data.definition: Represents the number of friendly personnel wounded in the reported action.

data.title: Friendly Losses-Missing in Action
data.definition: Represents the number of friendly personnel missing in the reported action.

data.title: Friendly Losses
data.definition: Repressents friendly losses (KIA, WIA, & MIA) resulting from the reported action.

data.title: Enemy Losses-Killed in Action
data.definition: Represents the number of enemy personnel killed in the reported action.

data.title: Enemy Losses-Prisoner of War
data.definition: Represents the number of enemy personnel made prisoner during the reported action.

data.title: Enemy Losses-Detained
data.definition: Represents the number of enemy personnel detained during the reported action.

data.title: Enemy Losses
data.definition: Represents enemy losses (KIA, POW, & DET) resulting from the reported action.

data.title: Individual Weapons Captured
data.definition: Indicates the number of individual type weapons captured during the reported action.

data.title: Crew Served Weapons Captured
data.definition: Indicates the number of crew served weapons captured during the reported action.

data.title: Weapons Captured
data.definition: Indicates the number of individual and crew served weapons captured during the reported action.

data.title: Service
data.definition: Identifies the service of the unit involved in the contact/incident action being reported.

data.title: Periodic Set 2 Group
data.definition: Represents Periodic Set 2

data.title: Periodic Set 2 Group with PSSQ2
data.definition: Represents Periodic Set 2, with PSSQ2. This group contains all the fields in Periodic Set 2 plus PSSQ2.

data.title: Weapon Size
data.definition: Defines the size and type artillery weapon used in support of an action.

data.title: Observed Mission
data.definition: Indicates the number of fire missions observed by friendly forces.

data.title: Unobserved Missions
data.definition: Indicates the number of artillery fire missions unobserved by friendly forces.

data.title: Harrassment and Interdiction Mission
data.definition: Indicates the number of harrassment and interdiction artillery fire missions executed.

data.title: Mission Type
data.definition: Indicates the number of artillery fire missions performed by type (observed, unobserved, harrassment and interdiction).

data.title: Missions in support of MAF
data.definition: Indicates the number of fire missions executed in support of MAF forces.

data.title: Missions in support of RVN
data.definition: Indicates the number of fire missions executed in support of RVN forces.

data.title: Missions in support of Other
data.definition: Indicates the number of fire missions executed in support of forces other than MAF and RVN.

data.title: Missions in Support
data.definition: Indicates the number of fire missions executed in support of MAF, RVN, and other forces.

data.title: Rounds Expenditure-High Explosive
data.definition: Indicates the number of rounds of high explosive (HE) ammunition expended in the support missions.

data.title: Rounds Expenditure-Illumination
data.definition: Indicates the number of rounds of illumination ammunition expended in the support missions.

data.title: Rounds Expenditure-Other
data.definition: Indicates the number of rounds of ammunition, other than HE and illumination, expended in the support missions.

data.title: Rounds Expenditure
data.definition: Indicates the number of HE (HERDS), Illumination (ILRDS), and other (OTRDS) rounds expended in support mission.

data.title: Periodic Set 3 Group
data.definition: Represents Periodic Set 3. This group contains all the fields in Periodic Set 3.

data.title: Periodic Set 3 Group with PSSQ3
data.definition: Represents Periodic Set 3, with PSSQ3. This group contains all the fields in Periodic Set 3 plus PSSQ3.
